{"tid":1816454,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"伊朗攻擊美軍基地 並警告美國不要採取報復，否則會襲擊美國本土","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T10:15:49.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4370d32e3226f4f0966ef88a9c3af5349750e47","tid":1816454,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=375932&amp;fbclid=IwAR3XV2B7dCZdrVsM4VTSLET8MDxPk0MJzIpO8yuHU0xiYKY8ly-GqRbkzWU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375932%26fbclid%3DIwAR3XV2B7dCZdrVsM4VTSLET8MDxPk0MJzIpO8yuHU0xiYKY8ly-GqRbkzWU&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=e1706c13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375932%26fbclid%3DIwAR3XV2B7dCZdrVsM4VTSLET8MDxPk0MJzIpO8yuHU0xiYKY8ly-GqRbkzWU&h=1b4bbb6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=375932&amp;fbclid=IwAR3XV2B7dCZdrVsM4VTSLET8MDxPk0MJzIpO8yuHU0xiYKY8ly-GqRbkzWU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2147-6/c0.10.540.282a/p540x282/82569735_1502665219883389_7217824057121570816_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQlUJ4nDKZdJWQcDsfhFA9vfnmxlhKU99ZZEXKX50DNsYfWBm-w4fnoyb952koQp5UY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=1&amp;oh=31fa03c3a035efba8bce6b1e6dd55982&amp;oe=5E92A999\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2147-6%2Fc0.10.540.282a%2Fp540x282%2F82569735_1502665219883389_7217824057121570816_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQlUJ4nDKZdJWQcDsfhFA9vfnmxlhKU99ZZEXKX50DNsYfWBm-w4fnoyb952koQp5UY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D1%26oh%3D31fa03c3a035efba8bce6b1e6dd55982%26oe%3D5E92A999&h=ae91d8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】伊朗發射導彈向駐伊拉克美軍發動至少兩輪攻擊，報復美軍日前擊殺革命衛隊將領索萊馬尼，據報伊拉克方面有人員傷亡。伊朗警告美國不要採取行動回應，否則會襲擊美國本土。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部證實，位於西部安巴爾省的阿薩德基地，及位於北部庫爾德族自治區埃爾比勒另一個基地，遭到伊朗十多枚彈道導彈攻擊，當局正評估受損及傷亡情況。<br />\n<br />\n有民眾拍攝到相信是阿薩德基地被伊朗導彈擊中的情況，伊朗國營電視台報道，革命衛隊航天師發起「烈士索萊馬尼行動」，向駐伊拉克美軍發動攻擊。在首輪攻擊後一小時，伊朗再發動第二輪攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗革命衛隊發聲明，警告美國及區內盟友不要報復，否則遭受毀滅性打擊，又說任何協助美國向伊朗進行攻擊的地方，都會成為伊朗打擊目標。<br />\n<br />\n白宮指總統特朗普已經知悉事件，正密切監察局勢，稍後將發表電視演說回應事件。"},{"pid":"72e5353ef387a3c1f120a24f419a3ab2c6ef588b","tid":1816454,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76b811329bc9e0106feabe8a01a7ee29fe2b719","tid":1816454,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9d45005cf12030c101e05bb83150570f8837d8","tid":1816454,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:22:06.000Z","msg":"無可能唔報復啦"},{"pid":"4bf73777f418999b0d56c710c425e79050195593","tid":1816454,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b9d45005cf12030c101e05bb83150570f8837d8","tid":1816454,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:22:06.000Z","msg":"無可能唔報復啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"紙老虎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea65451dd4e6c519f080e404cf821301796880a","tid":1816454,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"用咩打本土？<br />\n自殺式炸彈？"},{"pid":"3058091f4f3e84733594c2babcfb2d2a750936d8","tid":1816454,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:31:25.000Z","msg":"我發現極端主義既人  邏輯都特別D  其實有冇人明? 連阿拉都忍唔住手要地震教仔  佢叫人唔好報復佢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi